      {
        "id": 4,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 5,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "2nd Turning Point",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above This Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The lowest point in the story. The Protagonist has tried and failed to resolve the problem, but it looks as though all hope is lost as they face their worst-case scenario. They cannot solve the problem on their own; they need help in the form of new hope, ideas, new/returning Allies, or a personal change within themselves."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Deepen the problem and raise the stakes to make it appear as though all hope is lost (e.g. the issue with the landing gear is that it is broken, and the plane must be pulled from service, cancelling the flight. The next available flight leaves too late, and the funeral will be missed)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Identify a path forward for the Protagonist to resolve the problem (e.g. the Protagonist turns to the Ally that purchased the new ticket and enlists their assistance once more)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The 2nd Turning Point occurs around the 75% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
