        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "2nd Trigger Event",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above This Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Beginning of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The 2nd Triggering Event is a reversal of fortune in the story – though a lesser event than the 1st Triggering Event, it deepens the Protagonist's problem. It initiates downward action in the story once more, creating a new conflict or dilemma. The tension and the stakes are rising, leading to the lowest point in the story. "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce the 2nd Triggering event that threatens the Protagonist's goal once more (e.g. there is an announcement at the airport that there is an issue with the plane)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Increase drama and tension by raising the stakes and deepening the problem (e.g. the issue with the plane is broken landing gear)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The 2nd Triggering Event occurs around the 50% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
